---
import { Card, CardContent } from '../components/ui/card';
---

<section id="about" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-ink/10 py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-16 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-accent-light p-8 md:p-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-white/70">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-display mt-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl">
          Four high school students, one shared vision
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/80">
          <p>
            We created Aveira because we lived the problem. Late-night scrolling, lost sleep,
            groggy mornings. We wanted a real boundary between us and our phones - not another
            app, not a notification setting, but a physical object that changes behavior.
          </p>
          <p>
            Aveira detects your presence in the room using a radar sensor - no camera, no
            microphone. When it knows you're still awake past your set bedtime and your phone
            isn't docked, the alarm goes off. The only way to silence it is to place your
            phone on the dock.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <Card class="bg-[#927FB3]">
            <CardContent class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-10 text-center md:p-14">
              <span class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-accent md:text-6xl">4  </span>
              <span class="mt-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink md:text-sm">Students</span>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card class="bg-[#927FB3]">
            <CardContent class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-10 text-center md:p-14">
              <span class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-accent md:text-6xl">1  </span>
              <span class="mt-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink md:text-sm">Idea</span>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card class="bg-[#927FB3]">
            <CardContent class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-10 text-center md:p-14">
              <span class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-accent md:text-6xl">100%  </span>
              <span class="mt-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink md:text-sm">Privacy</span>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden border border-ink/10 bg-accent/[0.02] p-8 md:p-10">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-1 w-full bg-accent-light"></div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-light md:text-sm">The Mission</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold leading-relaxed text-ink/70 md:text-base">
            Every detail of Aveira is designed to make better sleep the path of least
            resistance. By replacing the constant struggle of willpower with a simple,
            physical boundary, it naturally helps you put down the screen so you can
            effortlessly transition into a restful night.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
